omendoza,

To seed just set the ratio of seeds in your torrent application to the number of times you want an item to seed - say 3 seeds, and then after the file has seeded to three other people it will become dimmed out (inactive) - you can delete the file - and you will no longer be a seeder.

If you want to seed unlimited - just select unlimited to the number of seeds, and let it go...
